These are Puzzles for 1x3 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-1::.
There 3 different types of food: peas, carrot, garlic
1. the person eating carrot is on the right of the person eating garlic##1
2. the person eating peas is on the far right##1
3. the person eating peas is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |    1    |       2       |   3   |
| Food   | garlic | carrot | peas |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-2::.
City: hamburg, paris, berlin
1. the person traveling to paris is in an odd position##4
2. the person traveling to hamburg is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |    1    |     2      |   3    |
| City   | hamburg | berlin | paris |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-3::.
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: dannemann, havana, prince
1. the havana-smoker is in an even position##4
2. the havana-smoker is on the left or right of the prince-smoker##3
3. the prince-smoker is on the right of the havana-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |    2    |      3       |
| Cigar   | dannemann | havana | prince |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-4::.
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: orchid, rose, poppy
1. the person who growsrose is in an odd position##4
2. the person who growspoppy is on the left of the person who growsrose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |   2    |  3   |
| Flower   | orchid | poppy | rose |

