.:: Puzzle 1x3-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: surfing, cricket, rugby
1. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who's sport is rugby##1
2. the person who's sport is cricket is on the far left or far right##3
3. the person who's sport is surfing is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|         |      1      |     2     |     3      |
| Sport   | cricket | rugby | surfing |

 